        "2.9 Crea una función llamada `imagenception()` que como argumento tenga la ruta de la imagen que quieres descifrar y que descifre la imagen secreta recientemente creada. Hint: Utiliza todos los pasos de la primera parte."
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {
        "Collapsed": "false",
        "id": "VR9TgJ-gs6xH"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "def imagenception(filepath):\n",
        "  secret_list = []\n",
        "  img = Image.open(filepath)\n",
        "  img_np = np.array(img)\n",
        "  for channel in range(img_np.shape[2]):\n",
        "    secret_aux = img_np[:,:,channel] % 2\n",
        "    secret_aux = secret_aux * 255\n",
        "    secret_aux = secret_aux.astype(np.uint8)\n",
        "    secret_list.append(secret_aux)\n",
        "  secret_np = np.concatenate(secret_list, axis=1)\n",
        "  secret_img = Image.fromarray(secret_np, mode=\"L\")\n",
        "  return secret_img"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {
        "Collapsed": "false",
        "id": "yl-QNr1os6xH"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "my_secret_img = imagenception(\"images/my_secret.png\")\n",
        "my_secret_img"
      ]
